# NexusLang v2 License Agreement

## Version 1.0 - November 2025

## Preamble

NexusLang v2 is an innovative AI-native programming language developed by Galion Studio. This license is designed to democratize AI development while protecting the commercial interests of the original creators and ensuring responsible use of advanced AI capabilities.

## 1. Definitions

- **"Software"** refers to NexusLang v2, its compiler, runtime, libraries, documentation, and all associated materials.
- **"Hobby Use"** means personal, educational, or non-commercial use with no revenue generation.
- **"Commercial Use"** means any use that generates revenue, provides services for payment, or is part of a commercial product.
- **"Developer Platform Member"** means any individual or entity registered on the official developer.galion.app platform.
- **"Heavy Modification"** means significant changes that alter the fundamental nature and functionality of the Software (more than 50% of the codebase).

## 2. Grant of License

### 2.1 Free Access
Subject to the terms of this license, you are granted a worldwide, royalty-free, non-exclusive license to:

- Use the Software for Hobby Use without any restrictions
- Modify the Software for your own Hobby Use
- Distribute Heavy Modifications of the Software for Hobby Use
- Access and use all libraries, APIs, and documentation

### 2.2 Commercial Use Restrictions
Commercial Use of the original Software (without Heavy Modification) requires explicit written permission from Galion Studio.

**To obtain commercial use permission:**
1. Send a notification to: licensing@galion.app
2. Include: your name, company (if applicable), intended use, and contact information
3. We will respond with approval within 5 business days
4. Upon approval, you receive full commercial rights for your specific use case

**Failure to obtain permission for Commercial Use violates this license.**

### 2.3 Developer Platform Exception

If you are a registered Developer Platform Member (developer.galion.app), you are granted additional rights:

#### 2.3.1 Full Access License
- **Complete Commercial Rights** - Use NexusLang v2 in any commercial application
- **No Permission Required** - Build and deploy commercial products without additional licensing
- **Platform Integration** - Access to Galion AI, personalities, and advanced features
- **Production Support** - Priority technical support and updates

#### 2.3.2 Platform Benefits
- **Nexus AI Access** - Full access to all AI models and personalities
- **Galion App Integration** - Commercial use rights for Galion platform
- **Voice-to-Voice APIs** - Unlimited commercial voice processing
- **Production Deployment** - Commercial deployment rights
- **API Monetization** - Rights to build commercial applications on our APIs

#### 2.3.3 Registration Process
1. Visit: https://developer.galion.app/auth/register
2. Create account (free)
3. Verify email
4. Gain immediate commercial rights
5. Access all platform features

